</div>
<button class="accordion">How does workplace violence affect employees?</button>
<div class="panel">
<p>Emotional problems resulting from violent incidents include self-doubt, depression, fear, post-traumatic stress syndrome, loss of sleep, irritation, disturbed relationships with family, friends and co-workers, decreased ability to function at work, and increased absenteeism.</p>
